  nnoremap <leader>wh <c-w>h
  nnoremap <leader>wj <c-w>j
  nnoremap <leader>wk <c-w>k

  " Easy pane resizing
  nnoremap <silent> <S-Left> 5<C-w>>
  nnoremap <silent> <S-Right> 5<C-w><
  nnoremap <silent> <S-Down> 5<C-W>-
  nnoremap <silent> <S-Up> 3<C-W>+
" }}}

